The paper discusses the challenges of interoperability in enterprise blockchain networks, which involves security, data transfer, and network consensus. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.CR (Cryptography and Security), followed by cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing), cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms), cs.SE (Software Engineering), and cs.DB (Databases).
